description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 Minute Stationary Bike Workout' from the channel Ryan Inlow.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Best Cardio Humanly Possible in 15 Minutes based on Dr Layne Norton's challenge.

read about it here:http://www.fitocracy.com/knowledge/dr-layne-nortons-best-damn-cardio-humanly-possible-in-15-minutes/...
